{"tid":175295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太陽能廠去年慘虧 134 億元，僅這幾家還獲利","createTime":"2017-03-27T11:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T08:23:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7beaac44828d5f84eaeb31d90701f03b4f65afc7","tid":175295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"2017 年 03 月 27 日 17:25 <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/shutterstock_180809807-624x441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fshutterstock_180809807-624x441.jpg&h=a3204774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太陽能產業景氣急轉直下，產品價格急遽滑落，國內太陽能矽晶圓與電池廠去年營運多面臨虧損窘境，估計總虧損金額達新台幣 134 億元，為歷年次高水準。<br />\n<br />\n隨著中國搶裝潮過後，去年下半年全球太陽能市場需求急凍，產品價格慘跌，衝擊太陽能廠去年營運普遍面臨虧損窘境，僅導電漿廠碩禾與電池廠元晶少數業者得以維持獲利狀態。<br />\n<br />\n太陽能電池廠新日光去年因產品價格下跌，加上進行中國及東南亞遷廠，並配合公司轉型提列資產減損和商譽損失，去年虧損 63 億元，創下歷史新高，並為去年虧損最多的太陽能廠。另一太陽能電池廠昱晶去年虧損 22.54 億元，虧損金額同創歷史新高紀錄，虧損超過半個股本。<br />\n<br />\n加計其餘太陽能矽晶圓與電池廠中美晶、綠能、茂迪、太極能源、昇陽光電與達能虧損，總虧損金額達 134 億元，為歷年次高水準，僅次於 2012 年的 211 億元。<br />\n<br />\n今年第一季因中國搶裝潮並未如預期湧現，產品價格表現不如預期，目前又逼近廠商成本線，法人預期，今年多數太陽能廠營運仍恐將持續面臨虧損考驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2017/03/27/solar-plants-taiwan-loss-2016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2Fsolar-plants-taiwan-loss-2016%2F&d=N9koirI5nbtQ%2BujBUnukpr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=46e714eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2017/03/27/solar-plants-taiwan-loss-2016/</a>"},{"pid":"2142b6c44a7cec6592d1dcd803c8444142e383b3","tid":175295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e14eebcf419070131ad3a240932522b071e0e82","tid":175295,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"環保撚出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdfa0ceaa989c13f1604daf8d6e6e42a920dd0b","tid":175295,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad76ac63a6bddb4054e9bb28d90fcbc86b996585","tid":175295,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"其實用太陽能，如計算所有成本，係咪仲貴？"},{"pid":"d54b1e28352dedcf79569482ba052d82d638eed8","tid":175295,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實用太陽能，如計算所有成本，係咪仲貴？</blockquote><br />\n成本都唔算問題,最大問題係唔夠地方"},{"pid":"51f8e04de7ac5540a8dd5c95b1c5a4893daef10a","tid":175295,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99952b7fcdd2f7d4aaf7b8c16c2e872c243ce872","tid":175295,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"碌撚"}]}